question: show me cumulative users over time
sql_query:
SELECT 
    DATE_TRUNC('month', created_at) AS month,
    COUNT(*) AS new_users,
    SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER (ORDER BY DATE_TRUNC('month', created_at)) AS cumulative_users
FROM users
GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('month', created_at)
ORDER BY month;

question: can you give me a number of all tenders posted in weekly buckets over past 3 month over time
sql_query:
SELECT 
    DATE_TRUNC('week', publication_date) AS week_start,
    COUNT(*) AS tender_count
FROM estonian_tender_details
WHERE publication_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3 months'
GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('week', publication_date)
ORDER BY week_start DESC;
